name: J'Quille (V)
Lore: 'Whiphid spy in league with Lady Valarian. Yearns for battle. Enjoys hearing the screams of his victims. Plotting to kill Jabba.',
Text: 'May deploy to a shielded site, and, for remainder of that turn, suspends ''Hoth Energy Shield Rules'' at his site. Once per game, when deployed to a site, opponent loses 1 Force for each Light Side character present.',
